1
00:00:04,120 --> 00:00:06,630
It couldn't be... Is she Earthland's...

2
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,890
She's... Edolas's me?

3
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:15,450
There she is!

4
00:00:15,450 --> 00:00:16,220
Over there!

5
00:00:16,750 --> 00:00:18,450
Let's discuss this later!

6
00:00:18,450 --> 00:00:21,250
We're going to be caught at this rate!

7
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:54,610
Natsu, hurry up and get them!

8
00:01:54,610 --> 00:01:55,790
How?

9
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:58,700
Use your magic, duh!

10
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:01,330
We can't <i>use</i> magic!

11
00:02:02,850 --> 00:02:05,780
And wait, why can <i>you</i> use it?

12
00:02:05,780 --> 00:02:07,020
How should I know?

13
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:09,010
Lucy, please!

14
00:02:09,010 --> 00:02:10,850
Get them!

15
00:02:10,850 --> 00:02:13,500
You're the only one who 
can use magic, Lucy-san!

16
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:18,150
Could it be? Am I the strongest now?

17
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:20,070
Whatever, just do it already!

18
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,630
Fireball!

19
00:02:26,380 --> 00:02:28,560
Gate of the Ram, I open thee!

20
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,580
Aries!

21
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:33,660
U-Um... I'll do my best...

22
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:34,730
I'm sorry!

23
00:02:34,730 --> 00:02:35,850
Poofy!

24
00:02:35,850 --> 00:02:37,550
W-What the hell is that?

25
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:38,600
A person appeared?

26
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,850
Is it an evil being?

27
00:02:39,850 --> 00:02:41,710
I've never seen magic like that before!

28
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:43,970
Aries, can you beat them?

29
00:02:43,970 --> 00:02:46,890
R-Right... I'll try!

30
00:02:46,890 --> 00:02:48,730
Wool Bomb!

31
00:02:49,350 --> 00:02:50,300
So soft...

32
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:51,570
I feel like a new man...

33
00:02:51,570 --> 00:02:54,220
Um, is this working?

34
00:02:54,220 --> 00:02:55,430
I'm sorry.

35
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:58,700
It's totally working! Keep attacking!

36
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:00,030
Wool Shot!

37
00:03:01,070 --> 00:03:02,630
Even though we're getting beat...

38
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:03,430
It feels good...

39
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:04,700
Do me more...

40
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:08,680
Wool Wall!

41
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:10,710
I could get used to this...

42
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,040
Now's our chance, everyone!

43
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,170
Did I do a good job?

44
00:03:16,170 --> 00:03:17,050
I'm sorry...

45
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:18,890
Poofy is the best!

46
00:03:18,890 --> 00:03:20,990
Nice, Lucy!

47
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:23,430
Ah, I think I feel good, too!

48
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:25,850
This is Earthland's magic?

49
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:32,910
We should be okay after 
running this far, right?

50
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:36,740
But, how did you get to Edolas?

51
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:42,150
We were all worried that you'd been 
turned into a lacrima, Lucy-san.

52
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:45,680
Horologium and Mystogan saved me.

53
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:47,410
Horologium?

54
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:48,870
Mystogan?

55
00:03:56,830 --> 00:03:58,390
What happened?

56
00:03:58,390 --> 00:04:00,670
Is this... Magnolia?

57
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:05,340
It was quite sudden, and I 
did not have time to explain.

58
00:04:05,790 --> 00:04:09,310
I am the one who saved you, Lucy-sama.

59
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:12,110
Saved me? What do you mean?

60
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:15,090
I sensed a fluctuation in space-time.

61
00:04:15,410 --> 00:04:17,860
I appeared without you summoning me,

62
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:20,740
and took you inside of me.

63
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:22,020
What about everyone else?

64
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:25,510
Where's Natsu, Erza, Gray, 
Wendy, and the others?

65
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:29,990
I apologize, but I do not understand 
what has happened myself.

66
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:32,950
Lucy, you are safe?

67
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:39,440
I am Mystogan.

68
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,530
Mystogan?

69
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:43,230
This is the first time we've 
greeted each other, yes?

70
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,880
Mystogan?

71
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:48,340
So that means he's safe, too?

72
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:51,480
Then, he explained what was going on to me.

73
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:55,940
Edolas? Another world?!

74
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,260
What the heck are you talking about?

75
00:04:58,260 --> 00:05:00,400
There is not time for a thorough explanation.

76
00:05:00,770 --> 00:05:04,530
If we do not hurry, the entrance 
to Edolas will seal off.

77
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:10,380
Wait a sec! You want me to 
go to this Edolas place?

78
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:13,750
Yes. I want you to save our friends.

79
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:17,830
I will search for anyone 
else who may have survived.

80
00:05:18,650 --> 00:05:19,710
Eat this.

81
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:21,990
What's that?

82
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:25,540
I don't have time to explain.

83
00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:26,430
Hurry!

84
00:05:26,790 --> 00:05:27,960
Wait a sec!

85
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:30,010
Give me more details!

86
00:05:30,990 --> 00:05:33,350
I'm counting on you, Lucy...

87
00:05:45,330 --> 00:05:48,310
This is... Edolas?

88
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:55,130
Since then, I've been searching 
the whole time for someone I know.

89
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:59,530
I wonder why Mystogan-san knew about Edolas?

90
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:01,630
Who exactly is he?

91
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:04,340
He didn't say anything at all...

92
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:10,700
Why is it that you're the only 
one who can use magic here, Lucy?

93
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:15,700
Maybe it's because I'm like, 
the legendary chosen warrior!

94
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:16,800
Not seeing it.

95
00:06:17,810 --> 00:06:19,230
So much for self-confidence...

96
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:22,610
Honestly, I don't know.

97
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:27,380
If you can't use magic, Natsu, then we're 
going to be at a real disadvantage...

98
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:36,320
You people seriously plan 
to go against the Kingdom?

99
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,480
Of course.

100
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,250
We'll do it for our friends!

101
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:43,620
Is that really me?

102
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:47,960
You can't even use magic for real, 
and you're fighting the Kingdom?

103
00:06:48,250 --> 00:06:50,930
Hey, I can use it!

104
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:56,200
Leave everything to Fairy Tail's 
(Currently) Strongest Wizard!

105
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,200
I'm all fired up!

106
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,450
I can't believe I'm saying this...

107
00:06:59,450 --> 00:07:00,980
...but we have no one else to turn to.

108
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:01,890
Aye!

109
00:07:01,890 --> 00:07:03,670
You can do it, Lucy-san!

110
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,730
What a bunch of weirdos...

111
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:12,390
Maybe these guys can 
actually change the world?

112
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:14,220
I get that feeling...

113
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:24,230
This is a map of Edolas I 
borrowed from the hotel.

114
00:07:24,230 --> 00:07:27,620
The geography isn't all that 
different from Earthland...

115
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:29,800
Edolas's Fairy Tail is here.

116
00:07:30,590 --> 00:07:33,570
We were chased by the frog around here...

117
00:07:33,570 --> 00:07:36,580
We ran into Lucy in the city of Louen.

118
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:40,080
And this is the city we're in now, Sycca.

119
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:43,390
Over here is the Royal City 
we are heading toward.

120
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:45,590
It's still quite a long way...

121
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:50,210
Plus, we have to be careful not to 
be discovered by the Royal Army...

122
00:07:50,210 --> 00:07:52,510
How long will it take to get there?

123
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:54,950
Hey, look at this!

124
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:59,880
She's exactly the same as me! 
Our bodies are identical!

125
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:02,550
Don't go prancing around in a towel!

126
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:05,820
Edo-Lucy-san, Natsu-san is here, you know!

127
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:08,190
And I should care, why?

128
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,340
Care, damn it!

129
00:08:10,340 --> 00:08:12,650
You're in high spirits, Doublucy!

130
00:08:12,650 --> 00:08:15,280
Are you actually proud of that joke?

131
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:20,250
What, Natsu? Wanna peek?

132
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:21,720
Please, stop it!

133
00:08:23,250 --> 00:08:25,160
What's so funny?

134
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:31,450
I know! You're trying to joke that 
Edo-Lucy's got a better figure than me, right?

135
00:08:32,230 --> 00:08:35,700
Don't take a bath together, sheesh!

136
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,450
Now that you mention it...

137
00:08:38,450 --> 00:08:42,050
They're so alike it's hard 
to even tell them apart...

138
00:08:42,050 --> 00:08:44,560
I couldn't believe we even have the same ass.

139
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,250
Please, stop it!

140
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:48,980
I bet you could do mirror acts and stuff!

141
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:50,140
No way!

142
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:52,180
They're like two peas in a pod...

143
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:53,510
Sad, really.

144
00:08:53,810 --> 00:08:56,600
Actually, it's like Gemini was summoned!

145
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,640
Oh, you're right.

146
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,800
Gemini?

147
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:02,010
They're a Spirit that I have a contract with!

148
00:09:02,010 --> 00:09:04,650
They can transform to look 
exactly like another person!

149
00:09:04,650 --> 00:09:06,690
Gate of the Twins, I open thee!

150
00:09:06,690 --> 00:09:07,480
Gemini!

151
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,840
Gemini is here!

152
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:15,270
Not Doublucy, but Triplucy!

153
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:19,320
Wow! We could do one of 
those party quiz games now!

154
00:09:19,770 --> 00:09:22,910
Quiz: Who is the real thing?

155
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:26,690
I'm Lucy!

156
00:09:26,690 --> 00:09:28,330
I'm Lucy!

157
00:09:28,330 --> 00:09:29,750
I'm Lucy!

158
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:32,990
Now, which one is the real one?

159
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,900
This isn't some party!

160
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:37,410
They're exactly in sync...

161
00:09:37,410 --> 00:09:38,770
Sad, really.

162
00:09:38,770 --> 00:09:40,820
And could you put some clothes on already?

163
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,650
I forgot!

164
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:49,250
It's only two of you now, but it's 
still hard to tell you apart.

165
00:09:49,250 --> 00:09:52,950
If I remember right, there was a Spirit 
that could change your hairstyle, right?

166
00:09:52,950 --> 00:09:55,860
Right! Let's ask the Spirit of the Crab!

167
00:09:56,610 --> 00:09:58,740
It is nice seeing you again-ebi.

168
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:01,000
He's a Crab Spirit, but ends 
his sentences with -ebi?

169
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,910
I knew you'd point that out!

170
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:03,950
You go, me!

171
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:10,540
How do you like it-ebi?

172
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:13,290
Yeah, this should make things a lot simpler.

173
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:17,640
Are you sure it's okay being this short?

174
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:22,080
Is there a custom on Earthland about 
taking care of your hair, too?

175
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:25,880
Well, all girls think like that-ebi.

176
00:10:26,230 --> 00:10:27,930
Girls, huh?

177
00:10:31,110 --> 00:10:36,440
You'd just be stupid to think of being 
a "boy" or a "girl" in this world...

178
00:10:37,010 --> 00:10:39,950
We've got enough to handle just surviving...

179
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:46,130
But everyone in the guild here 
looked like they were having fun...

180
00:10:46,130 --> 00:10:47,800
Well, sure.

181
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:51,900
If we didn't force ourselves to keep 
laughing, our hearts would break just like that...

182
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:56,590
Plus, there are people who still 
need us, even in this world.

183
00:10:57,080 --> 00:11:02,180
So, even if we're now "Dark", 
we're got to keep the guild going.

184
00:11:04,950 --> 00:11:07,680
But I guess that by itself 
isn't going to cut it...

185
00:11:10,450 --> 00:11:11,880
Nothing...

186
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,260
I can't believe this!

187
00:11:17,260 --> 00:11:19,140
What the heck is this?

188
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:21,810
Do you <i>have</i> to be so hyped 
up this early in the morning?

189
00:11:21,810 --> 00:11:23,140
What is it?

190
00:11:23,140 --> 00:11:25,960
The Edolas me ran away!

191
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:29,620
"If you walk for three days to the 
east, you'll reach the Royal City."

192
00:11:29,620 --> 00:11:31,810
"I'm returning to the guild."

193
00:11:31,810 --> 00:11:33,540
"Later. I wish you the best of luck."

194
00:11:33,540 --> 00:11:36,000
I thought she was going to help us!

195
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,710
What nerve!

196
00:11:38,710 --> 00:11:40,780
The same nerve as you Lucy, right?

197
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:41,670
Shut it!

198
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:47,120
We can't do anything about it. She said 
she didn't intend to fight from the start.

199
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:47,890
Yeah...

200
00:11:48,410 --> 00:11:52,580
I won't forgive her! I wouldn't forgive 
myself, so I won't forgive her!

201
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:54,970
Why does it matter, really?

202
00:11:54,970 --> 00:11:57,500
It does matter! Argh!

203
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:02,430
Do I really think those 
people can change the world?

204
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:06,670
What silly nonsense was I thinking...?

205
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:11,620
If I really want to change the world, what's 
the point if we don't do it ourselves?

206
00:12:12,250 --> 00:12:16,030
It'll be great if they can use 
their power to save their friends,

207
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:19,130
but that'll be difficult against the Kingdom.

208
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:22,590
So I'm going to go back to the 
guild and convince everyone.

209
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:27,280
Everyone, stand up! We'll 
fight alongside them!

210
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:39,790
Did you hear?

211
00:12:39,790 --> 00:12:43,090
Sounds like they're gonna start extracting 
the magic power from that lacrima in two days.

212
00:12:43,090 --> 00:12:45,040
Oh... I don't really get it,

213
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:49,130
but you're talking about all the magic power 
they scooped up from that other world, right?

214
00:12:49,130 --> 00:12:51,230
Is this really gonna be okay?

215
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:53,370
I just hope nothin' screwy 
happens as a result...

216
00:12:53,710 --> 00:12:57,950
What? Are you saying there's something 
wrong with the King's methods?

217
00:12:57,950 --> 00:13:00,290
Oh no, I didn't mean that...

218
00:13:00,290 --> 00:13:03,130
We should just leave this 
all to His Highness.

219
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:06,760
People like us worryin' 
ain't gonna do anything.

220
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,680
About that...

221
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,680
About that...

222
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,940
Would you tell me more?

223
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,940
Could you tell me more?

224
00:13:16,690 --> 00:13:18,810
She's already back in high spirits.

225
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:22,690
She's happy she found that rare 
book at the bookstore, right?

226
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:25,670
What kind of book did you buy?

227
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,710
A book on the history of this world!

228
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:31,660
I bet you guys want to learn 
about this world too, right?

229
00:13:31,660 --> 00:13:32,730
Not really.

230
00:13:32,950 --> 00:13:35,090
This history book tells everything!

231
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:37,340
This world is fascinating!

232
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:41,560
For example, the "Exceed" race 
is written about in here...

233
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:44,280
I'd like to know about that, too.

234
00:13:44,530 --> 00:13:47,640
They seem like a race that is 
extremely feared, though...

235
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,110
I said I don't care.

236
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:53,680
What's this?

237
00:13:53,950 --> 00:13:54,850
That's...!

238
00:13:56,250 --> 00:13:57,560
An airship?

239
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:58,650
Hurry!

240
00:13:58,650 --> 00:13:59,940
We're taking off!

241
00:14:00,190 --> 00:14:01,590
It's the Royal Army!

242
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:02,460
Hide!

243
00:14:04,110 --> 00:14:06,340
They're finally going to 
extract the magic power

244
00:14:06,340 --> 00:14:08,480
from that giant lacrima 
the day after tomorrow!

245
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:11,490
And so that's why we've 
been put on guard duty.

246
00:14:11,490 --> 00:14:15,140
You don't get on board, you'll 
miss the event of a lifetime!

247
00:14:15,950 --> 00:14:17,840
Giant lacrima, they say?

248
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,920
That's everyone from Magnolia...

249
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:22,280
They're extracting the magic 
power two days from now?

250
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:24,460
We won't make it in time if we walk!

251
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:30,090
If they start extracting the magic 
power, everyone will be gone for good.

252
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,500
Can we steal that ship?

253
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:36,580
Steal it?

254
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:37,850
That airship?

255
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:39,980
Normally, that's not necessary, right?

256
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:42,140
Just sneaking on board should be fine!

257
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:43,790
I hate hiding.

258
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:47,400
It's rare for you to suggest 
transportation, Natsu...

259
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:51,950
As long as I have Wendy's 
Troia, riding stuff is...

260
00:14:51,950 --> 00:14:54,510
We can't use magic, remember?

261
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,080
I take that plan back.

262
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:57,340
Hey!

263
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,910
Well, I vote we do it!

264
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:04,170
We won't make it otherwise, right?

265
00:15:04,170 --> 00:15:06,010
But, how?

266
00:15:06,010 --> 00:15:07,680
With my magic!

267
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:11,070
You remember, right? I'm 
the strongest right now!

268
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:15,730
I figured it out when fighting in Louen.

269
00:15:15,730 --> 00:15:19,750
Basically, magic is more advanced 
on Earthland than it is here.

270
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:21,780
That's probably true, yeah.

271
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:26,190
Now, watch!

272
00:15:27,370 --> 00:15:29,630
Gate of the Lion, I open thee!

273
00:15:29,630 --> 00:15:30,400
Loke!

274
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:32,440
Huh?

275
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:34,860
I apologize, Princess.

276
00:15:34,860 --> 00:15:35,960
Virgo?

277
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,980
Wait, what's going on?

278
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:41,790
Brother is on a date, and cannot 
be summoned at the moment.

279
00:15:42,350 --> 00:15:43,720
Brother?

280
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:47,150
Yes. Leo-sama requested I 
address him that way earlier.

281
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:49,710
He's such an idiot!

282
00:15:49,710 --> 00:15:51,290
That's Lucy!

283
00:15:51,290 --> 00:15:52,510
Capture her!

284
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:57,740
Crap! I figured that Loke 
would beat them all!

285
00:15:57,740 --> 00:16:00,720
Princess... With your permission, 
if I use my full power...

286
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:02,850
...I can even dance!

287
00:16:02,850 --> 00:16:03,730
Go away!

288
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:07,610
Lucy, what if you bring out Aquarius?

289
00:16:07,610 --> 00:16:09,250
There's no water here!

290
00:16:09,250 --> 00:16:10,140
Taurus?

291
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:11,790
It's too late!

292
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:12,950
What'll I do?!

293
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:16,330
Guess we have no choice, but 
to play by their rules...

294
00:16:16,330 --> 00:16:18,410
I know how to use it now!

295
00:16:18,410 --> 00:16:20,370
The magic we bought in the black market!

296
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:26,090
Natsu and Wendy are completely useless!

297
00:16:26,090 --> 00:16:27,810
Better than Lucy, though.

298
00:16:27,810 --> 00:16:29,730
I'm sorry!

299
00:16:29,730 --> 00:16:31,260
This is bad! The airship is leaving!

300
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:36,050
We'll never make it unless we get on board!

301
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:37,930
Damn it!

302
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,070
What?

303
00:16:58,650 --> 00:17:00,110
A magic 4-wheeler?

304
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:02,410
That's Fairy Tail's mark!

305
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:07,710
I heard from Lucy. Get in.

306
00:17:09,150 --> 00:17:10,880
We're gonna fly. Don't fall out.

307
00:17:12,170 --> 00:17:14,250
Go Fire!

308
00:17:20,140 --> 00:17:26,600
So in other words, you were sent here 
to this world by a certain Mystogan-san?

309
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:29,580
He gave me a brief explanation.

310
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:33,400
But I don't really understand 
things over here.

311
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:38,040
This is a most interesting tale.

312
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:40,780
Tell me something, me 
who's from this world...

313
00:17:42,700 --> 00:17:45,890
What is it, myself from that other world?

314
00:17:45,890 --> 00:17:49,250
You're a freelance writer 
here in Edolas, right?

315
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:55,100
Yes. My job is to investigate thoroughly 
what happens in this world and to write about it.

316
00:17:55,790 --> 00:17:58,590
You seem to have a lot of enemies out there.

317
00:17:59,100 --> 00:18:02,850
I was attacked by some strange 
guys who mistook me for you.

318
00:18:03,410 --> 00:18:08,480
I do very much apologize for 
causing you such trouble.

319
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:13,300
There are indeed those who 
consider me quite the eyesore.

320
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:17,500
Since I write about things which are not 
in the Kingdom or government's favor.

321
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:20,610
However, I do not write 
articles which are false.

322
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:28,120
I heard that there was a lot different 
between this and my original world.

323
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,630
But we're not that different 
after all, are we?

324
00:18:32,090 --> 00:18:37,550
You're polite and cultured, just like me!

325
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:42,510
And I think your wild and cool 
charms are precisely like my own!

326
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:46,520
You should know that I am very talented 
at singing and musical instruments.

327
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:50,390
Oh! That's another thing we have in common!

328
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:57,780
A number of my buddies should 
be coming through here.

329
00:18:58,690 --> 00:19:01,410
I'm sure they'll cause a 
big commotion before long.

330
00:19:01,850 --> 00:19:02,920
And then...

331
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:05,370
Sure. I'll let you know right away.

332
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:11,130
My information network has its fingers 
even inside the Kingdom and the Exceed...

333
00:19:11,570 --> 00:19:15,240
I'm counting on you. We'll 
make our move based on that.

334
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:17,550
Be careful.

335
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,580
Same to you.

336
00:19:23,510 --> 00:19:27,230
Wow! We escaped just like that!

337
00:19:27,230 --> 00:19:28,520
You saved us...

338
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:30,190
Thank you very much!

339
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:34,860
You're going to the Royal City, right?

340
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:38,610
This'll be faster than that beat-up airship.

341
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:42,610
The fastest man in Fairy Tail...

342
00:19:44,250 --> 00:19:47,830
That's me, "Fireball" Natsu.

343
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,960
Natsu?!

344
00:19:52,150 --> 00:19:53,180
Natsu!

345
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:56,080
This is... Edolas's Natsu?

346
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:59,930
Just like Lucy said... The spittin' image.

347
00:19:59,930 --> 00:20:02,380
And that's the other me?

348
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:03,930
Lame...

349
00:20:05,430 --> 00:20:09,400
Our Natsu can't handle transportation.

350
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:11,370
Is that really supposed to be me?

351
00:20:11,370 --> 00:20:16,860
Just like my nickname, "Fireball", I'm 
a wizard that specializes in deliveries.

352
00:20:18,650 --> 00:20:22,080
This magic 4-wheeler doesn't have a SE plug!

353
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,750
SE plug?

354
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,680
Self Energy plug.

355
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:28,830
It's a device that converts the 
magic power of the driver into fuel.

356
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:32,380
That's right... People don't have 
magic power themselves here,

357
00:20:32,380 --> 00:20:34,550
so there's no point having a SE plug.

358
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:37,530
So then it just runs on magic alone?

359
00:20:37,530 --> 00:20:42,800
Oh? Looks like Edolas's cars are way 
more advanced than Earthland's...

360
00:20:48,350 --> 00:20:50,650
Hey, what was that all of a sudden?

361
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,960
I wouldn't say that.

362
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:58,980
As magic power is a limited resource, 
so is the magic power for fuel.

363
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:01,890
It's tricky to get now.

364
00:21:02,530 --> 00:21:05,830
So, this is as far as I take you.

365
00:21:06,540 --> 00:21:07,110
Get out.

366
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:11,910
If I go any further, I won't 
make it back to the guild.

367
00:21:12,620 --> 00:21:16,320
They went and transferred somewhere again...

368
00:21:18,830 --> 00:21:21,090
I'm alive again!

369
00:21:21,090 --> 00:21:24,590
Looks like the other me catches on fast!

370
00:21:25,630 --> 00:21:28,320
Now, everyone out!

371
00:21:29,550 --> 00:21:32,240
Go right ahead and fight 
against the Kingdom...

372
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:34,100
But don't get us involved.

373
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,410
This time, since Lucy...

374
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:39,050
Not you.

375
00:21:39,050 --> 00:21:43,230
Since the Lucy <i>I</i> know asked 
me, I lent you a hand.

376
00:21:43,700 --> 00:21:45,740
But I'm not going to get my hands dirty.

377
00:21:46,300 --> 00:21:49,590
I just want to continue cruising...

378
00:21:50,300 --> 00:21:51,240
Hey!

379
00:21:54,260 --> 00:21:55,700
You get out, too!

380
00:21:56,610 --> 00:21:58,110
Hey, what the hell are you...

381
00:21:58,110 --> 00:22:00,540
I have something to say to you, other me!

382
00:22:00,540 --> 00:22:03,120
Stop it! L-Let me go!

383
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:04,920
Put me down!

384
00:22:07,150 --> 00:22:08,430
You...

385
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,730
How can you handle transportation like that?!

386
00:22:11,730 --> 00:22:13,120
That's what he says?!

387
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:20,430
I'm sorry!

388
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:23,760
I don't know either!

389
00:23:55,700 --> 00:23:58,440
Oh yeah, this is your homeland, right, Happy?

390
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,570
Does anything ring a bell?

391
00:24:00,570 --> 00:24:03,560
No bells ringing here! I was 
still in an egg back then.

392
00:24:03,560 --> 00:24:05,390
Well, you have a point!

393
00:24:05,390 --> 00:24:08,000
Wait, then why does Carla 
know a bunch of stuff?

394
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:10,810
Maybe she had special Eggucation?

395
00:24:10,810 --> 00:24:14,000
Wow, Edolas sure is advanced!

396
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:16,550
Next time: Welcome Home!

397
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:20,890
But my only homeland is 
Earthland's Fairy Tail!

398
00:24:20,890 --> 00:24:22,750
You said it, buddy!

399
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:24,940
I wonder if my approval rating just went up?

